{
  "page": "House Pyle",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Pyle</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Pyle.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Pyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/250px-House_Pyle.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/375px-House_Pyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/500px-House_Pyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA grey iron greathelm on white<br /><i>(Argent, an iron greathelm cendrée)</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Pyle</b> is a noble house from the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a>. According to semi-canon sources they blazon their arms with a grey iron greathelm on white.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#House_Pyle_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Pyle at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Historical_Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Pyle_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Pyle at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Pyle at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Pyles during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>no member has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Howard_Pyle\" title=\"Howard Pyle\">Howard Pyle</a>, attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>House Pyle may be a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to illustrator and author <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Howard_Pyle\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Howard Pyle\">Howard Pyle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/1/\">Houses in the area of King's Landing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (Graphic Novel)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_A_Blog\" title=\"Not A Blog\">Not A Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2013/03/13/reading-recommendations/\